| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-5303 — Recovery Inhibition (malekteam)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 57bdabcc-9bdf-58ce-ae1f-4ab6ee3be44b"
